---
// Contact.astro
---

<section id="contact" class="section-pad wrap contact">
  <span class="eyebrow reveal" style="justify-content:center">Contact</span>

  <h2 class="big reveal" data-d="2" style="margin-top:24px">
    Let's build<br/>
    <a href="mailto:halo@isnaeni.dev" data-magnetic="0.15" id="contact-email">something great</a>
  </h2>

  <p class="contact-sub reveal" data-d="2">
    Punya ide produk, butuh fitur AI, atau sekadar ingin ngobrol soal engineering? Pintu saya terbuka.
  </p>

  <div class="socials reveal" data-d="3">
    <a
      class="social"
      href="mailto:halo@isnaeni.dev"
      data-magnetic="0.3"
      id="social-email"
      aria-label="Send email to Isnaeni Hidayat"
    >
      ✉ Email
    </a>
    <a
      class="social"
      href="https://github.com/isnaenihidayat"
      target="_blank"
      rel="noopener noreferrer"
      data-magnetic="0.3"
      id="social-github"
      aria-label="Visit GitHub profile (opens in new tab)"
    >
      ⌥ GitHub
    </a>
    <a
      class="social"
      href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/isnaeni-hidayat/"
      target="_blank"
      rel="noopener noreferrer"
      data-magnetic="0.3"
      id="social-linkedin"
      aria-label="Visit LinkedIn profile (opens in new tab)"
    >
      in LinkedIn
    </a>
  </div>
</section>
